{"tid":1360194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句到尾 如果有雙普選仲獨唔獨立","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:27:38.000Z","uid":6609,"like":327,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c8df12f1db0536d8cb1d33746ae9fc503520eb","tid":1360194,"uid":6609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"其實呢個幾月黎 我哋嘅矛頭一直都係呢個政權<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果</span></span></strong>他朝有一日我哋真係可以迫使中共履行基本法入邊嘅承諾 喺香港實行雙普選 咁之後條路應該點行呢 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算</span></span></strong>有雙普選 但係香港咁多廢中廢老深藍 難保他日又選咗個中共派黎嘅做香港話事人（你睇年年咁多民建聯嘅人立法會就知）咁到時又應該點拆呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母 老閪都要獨立 就算有雙普選都係比中共騎住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雙普選就係我哋最終目的 有得一人一票選特首就唔驚中共lu<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>頭盔：非分化 不割𥱊 槍口對準</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3106fdcdc0cf2aa9fb1891ad393f2263d62434ef","tid":1360194,"uid":6609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txB5Mtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtxB5Mtw.png&h=deec6700&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3df776ba8b6dede3ef440552aa5a5c0264d14237","tid":1360194,"uid":6609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4b5a21851764891e5e4f01a093849992428c5df","tid":1360194,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"目前情況佢出呢個offer我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果到時連藍絲都反緊 6-7成人都屌緊就梗係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0defa54253011f110a58bd0987051bb744c56ac","tid":1360194,"uid":21920,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"c